body:
title pretty much explains itself, i was trying to buy katarina and she costs 3150 ip, i can clearly afford her but every time i hover over her the box greys out and it says i dont have enough rp/ip to buy her. I've asked many different people in game to see if this was a problem on my side but many have the same problem. I tried everything i could to fix this problem, even the full repair available from the settings but nothing seems to work. This is clearly a server-side error that needs to be fixed, ty.

Oh yeah, and some free RP would be nice :). jk...plez
